---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: /feeds-mock/index.html
hide_newsletter: true
---

{% set sample = speakerFeeds.entries | slice(6) | first %}

<style>
  .mock {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 32px;
  }
  .mock h1 { margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .mock .lede { color: var(--dark-grey); margin: 0 0 40px 0; max-width: 60ch; }

  .variant {
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }
  .variant header {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--light-grey);
    padding-bottom: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .variant h2 {
    font-size: 22px;
    margin: 0 0 4px 0;
  }
  .variant .note {
    color: var(--dark-grey);
    font-size: 14px;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  @media (min-width: 720px) {
    .grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }

  /* ---------- Variant A: stripped ---------- */
  .va {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 64px 1fr auto;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    border: 1px solid var(--light-grey);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: white;
  }
  .va img { width: 64px; height: 64px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; display: block; }
  .va .who { min-width: 0; }
  .va .who h3 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--primary);
    line-height: 1.25;
  }
  .va .who p {
    margin: 2px 0 0 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--dark-grey);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .va .who a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
  .va .who a:hover { color: var(--salmon); }
  .va .feed-link {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .va .feed-link:hover { color: var(--salmon); }

  /* ---------- Variant B: name-forward, no photo frame ---------- */
  .vb {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    align-items: start;
    gap: 8px 24px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: var(--box);
  }
  .vb h3 {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--primary);
    line-height: 1.15;
  }
  .vb p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--dark-grey);
    line-height: 1.35;
  }
  .vb a.homepage {
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    text-decoration-color: var(--light-grey);
  }
  .vb a.homepage:hover { color: var(--salmon); text-decoration-color: currentColor; }
  .vb .sub {
    padding: 8px 16px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    white-space: nowrap;
    align-self: start;
  }
  .vb .sub:hover { background: var(--salmon); color: white; }

  /* ---------- Variant C: latest-post forward ---------- */
  .vc {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 56px 1fr;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--light-grey);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: white;
  }
  .vc img { width: 56px; height: 56px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; display: block; }
  .vc .body { min-width: 0; }
  .vc .who {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .vc .who h3 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--primary);
    line-height: 1.2;
    min-width: 0;
  }
  .vc .icon-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 4px;
    flex: 0 0 auto;
  }
  .vc .icon-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    color: var(--dark-grey);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 80ms ease-out, background 80ms ease-out;
  }
  .vc .icon-btn:hover {
    color: var(--primary);
    background: var(--box);
  }
  .vc .icon-btn svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; display: block; }
  .vc .body .talk {
    margin: 2px 0 10px 0;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--dark-grey);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .vc .latest {
    display: block;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    background: var(--box);
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--primary);
  }
  .vc .latest:hover { background: var(--light-grey); }
  .vc .latest .label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--dark-grey);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .vc .latest .title {
    display: block;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  /* ---------- Variant E: C + selectable ---------- */
  .ve {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 56px 1fr;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 16px;
    padding-right: 52px;
    border: 1px solid var(--light-grey);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: white;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: border-color 80ms ease-out, box-shadow 80ms ease-out;
  }
  .ve:hover { border-color: var(--dark-grey); }
  .ve.selected { border-color: var(--salmon); box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--salmon); }
  .ve img { width: 56px; height: 56px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; display: block; }
  .ve .body { min-width: 0; }
  .ve .who { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
  .ve .who h3 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--primary);
    line-height: 1.2;
    min-width: 0;
    flex: 1 1 auto;
  }
  .ve .who h3 .year {
    font-weight: normal;
    color: var(--dark-grey);
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-left: 2px;
  }
  .ve .icon-row { display: flex; gap: 2px; flex: 0 0 auto; }
  .ve .icon-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 26px;
    height: 26px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    color: var(--dark-grey);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 80ms ease-out, background 80ms ease-out;
  }
  .ve .icon-btn:hover { color: var(--primary); background: var(--box); }
  .ve .icon-btn svg { width: 15px; height: 15px; display: block; }
  .ve .talk {
    margin: 2px 0 10px 0;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--dark-grey);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .ve .latest {
    display: block;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    background: var(--box);
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--primary);
  }
  .ve .latest:hover { background: var(--light-grey); }
  .ve .latest .meta {
    display: block;
  }
  .ve .latest .label {
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--dark-grey);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .ve .latest .date {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--dark-grey);
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .ve .latest .date::before {
    content: ' · ';
  }
  .ve .latest .title {
    display: block;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .ve .check {
    position: absolute;
    top: 16px;
    right: 16px;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border: 2px solid var(--light-grey);
    border-radius: 5px;
    background: white;
    transition: all 60ms ease-out;
  }
  .ve:hover .check { border-color: var(--dark-grey); }
  .ve.selected .check {
    background: var(--salmon);
    border-color: var(--salmon);
    position: absolute;
  }
  .ve.selected .check::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='white' stroke-width='3' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round'><polyline points='5 12 10 17 19 7'/></svg>");
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
    background-size: 14px;
  }

  /* ---------- Variant F: minimal selectable + icons ---------- */
  .vf {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr auto;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    border: 1px solid var(--light-grey);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: white;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: border-color 80ms ease-out, box-shadow 80ms ease-out;
  }
  .vf:hover { border-color: var(--dark-grey); }
  .vf.selected { border-color: var(--salmon); box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--salmon); }
  .vf img { width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; display: block; }
  .vf .who { min-width: 0; }
  .vf .who h3 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--primary);
    line-height: 1.25;
  }
  .vf .who p {
    margin: 2px 0 0 0;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--dark-grey);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .vf .actions { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; }
  .vf .icon-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    color: var(--dark-grey);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 80ms ease-out, background 80ms ease-out;
  }
  .vf .icon-btn:hover { color: var(--primary); background: var(--box); }
  .vf .icon-btn svg { width: 15px; height: 15px; display: block; }
  .vf .check {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border: 2px solid var(--light-grey);
    border-radius: 5px;
    background: white;
    margin-left: 4px;
    transition: all 60ms ease-out;
  }
  .vf:hover .check { border-color: var(--dark-grey); }
  .vf.selected .check {
    background: var(--salmon);
    border-color: var(--salmon);
    position: relative;
  }
  .vf.selected .check::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='white' stroke-width='3' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round'><polyline points='5 12 10 17 19 7'/></svg>");
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
    background-size: 14px;
  }

  /* ---------- Variant D: card-as-action ---------- */
  .vd {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr 24px;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    border: 1px solid var(--light-grey);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: white;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 80ms ease-out;
  }
  .vd:hover { background: var(--box); }
  .vd img { width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; display: block; }
  .vd .who { min-width: 0; }
  .vd .who h3 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--primary);
    line-height: 1.25;
  }
  .vd .who p {
    margin: 2px 0 0 0;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--dark-grey);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .vd .check {
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
    border: 2px solid var(--light-grey);
    border-radius: 5px;
    background: white;
  }
  .vd.selected { border-color: var(--salmon); box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--salmon); background: white; }
  .vd.selected .check { background: var(--salmon); border-color: var(--salmon); position: relative; }
  .vd.selected .check::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='white' stroke-width='3' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round'><polyline points='5 12 10 17 19 7'/></svg>");
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center;
    background-size: 14px;
  }
</style>

<section class="mock">
  <h1>Feed card mock-ups</h1>
  <p class="lede">Four directions for tightening the speaker feed card. Not production — a sandbox to see shapes at real data density before picking one. Each uses the same four speakers.</p>

  {% set picks = speakerFeeds.entries | slice(4) | first %}

  <section class="variant">
    <header>
      <h2>A — Row, stripped</h2>
      <p class="note">Current card minus the pills and divider. One name size, one muted talk-title line, homepage as the single action. Photo circle. Good if you want the least visual change.</p>
    </header>
    <div class="grid">
      {% for i in range(0, 4) %}
      {% set entry = speakerFeeds.entries[i] %}
      <div class="va">
        <img src="{{ entry.photo }}" alt="" loading="lazy">
        <div class="who">
          <h3><a href="/talks/{{ entry.talk.slug }}/">{{ entry.name }}</a></h3>
          <p>{{ entry.talk.title }}</p>
        </div>
        <a class="feed-link" href="{{ entry.feed }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RSS →</a>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="variant">
    <header>
      <h2>B — Name-forward, soft tile</h2>
      <p class="note">No photo. Big speaker name, talk as caption, subscribe pill on the right. Reads like a directory list. Loses photo recognition but much calmer — fewer things to scan per card.</p>
    </header>
    <div class="grid">
      {% for i in range(0, 4) %}
      {% set entry = speakerFeeds.entries[i] %}
      <div class="vb">
        <h3>{{ entry.name }}</h3>
        <p><a class="homepage" href="{{ entry.homepage }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ entry.homepage | replace('https://', '') | replace('http://', '') | replace(r/\/$/, '') }}</a></p>
        <a class="sub" href="{{ entry.feed }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Subscribe</a>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="variant">
    <header>
      <h2>C — Latest post forward</h2>
      <p class="note">Puts the latest blog-post title on the card. Answers "why would I subscribe?" without me having to click through. Homepage + RSS as icon buttons in the top-right; talk title shrinks to muted caption since it's secondary here.</p>
    </header>
    <div class="grid">
      {% for i in range(0, 4) %}
      {% set entry = speakerFeeds.entries[i] %}
      <div class="vc">
        <img src="{{ entry.photo }}" alt="" loading="lazy">
        <div class="body">
          <div class="who">
            <h3>{{ entry.name }}</h3>
            <div class="icon-row">
              <a class="icon-btn" href="{{ entry.homepage }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="{{ entry.name }}'s homepage" title="Homepage">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
                  <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/>
                  <path d="M3 12h18"/>
                  <path d="M12 3a14 14 0 0 1 4 9 14 14 0 0 1-4 9 14 14 0 0 1-4-9 14 14 0 0 1 4-9z"/>
                </svg>
              </a>
              <a class="icon-btn" href="{{ entry.feed }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="{{ entry.name }}'s RSS feed" title="RSS feed">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path d="M6.18 15.64a2.18 2.18 0 1 1 0 4.36 2.18 2.18 0 0 1 0-4.36zM4 4.44A.44.44 0 0 1 4.44 4c8.6 0 15.56 6.96 15.56 15.56a.44.44 0 0 1-.44.44h-2.83a.44.44 0 0 1-.44-.42A11.85 11.85 0 0 0 4.42 7.71.44.44 0 0 1 4 7.27V4.44zm0 5.66a.44.44 0 0 1 .44-.44c5.45 0 9.87 4.42 9.9 9.87a.44.44 0 0 1-.44.43h-2.83a.44.44 0 0 1-.44-.43 6.2 6.2 0 0 0-6.19-6.18A.44.44 0 0 1 4 12.93V10.1z"/>
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="talk">{{ entry.talk.title }} · {{ entry.talk.year }}</p>
          {% if entry.latest %}
          <a class="latest" href="{{ entry.latest.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <span class="label">Latest post</span>
            <span class="title">{{ entry.latest.title }}</span>
          </a>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

  {% set iconGlobe %}<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M3 12h18"/><path d="M12 3a14 14 0 0 1 4 9 14 14 0 0 1-4 9 14 14 0 0 1-4-9 14 14 0 0 1 4-9z"/></svg>{% endset %}
  {% set iconRss %}<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6.18 15.64a2.18 2.18 0 1 1 0 4.36 2.18 2.18 0 0 1 0-4.36zM4 4.44A.44.44 0 0 1 4.44 4c8.6 0 15.56 6.96 15.56 15.56a.44.44 0 0 1-.44.44h-2.83a.44.44 0 0 1-.44-.42A11.85 11.85 0 0 0 4.42 7.71.44.44 0 0 1 4 7.27V4.44zm0 5.66a.44.44 0 0 1 .44-.44c5.45 0 9.87 4.42 9.9 9.87a.44.44 0 0 1-.44.43h-2.83a.44.44 0 0 1-.44-.43 6.2 6.2 0 0 0-6.19-6.18A.44.44 0 0 1 4 12.93V10.1z"/></svg>{% endset %}

  <section class="variant">
    <header>
      <h2>E — C plus selectable card</h2>
      <p class="note">Latest post + icon buttons from C, but the whole card is a selection target with a checkmark in the top-right. Clicking the photo or card toggles selection; icons and latest-post link are click-through.</p>
    </header>
    <div class="grid">
      {% for i in range(0, 4) %}
      {% set entry = speakerFeeds.entries[i] %}
      <div class="ve" data-toggle>
        <img src="{{ entry.photo }}" alt="" loading="lazy">
        <div class="body">
          <div class="who">
            <h3>{{ entry.name }} <span class="year">· {{ entry.talk.year }}</span></h3>
            <div class="icon-row">
              <a class="icon-btn" href="{{ entry.homepage }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="{{ entry.name }}'s homepage" title="Homepage">{{ iconGlobe | safe }}</a>
              <a class="icon-btn" href="{{ entry.feed }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="{{ entry.name }}'s RSS feed" title="RSS feed">{{ iconRss | safe }}</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="talk">{{ entry.talk.title }}</p>
          {% if entry.latest %}
          <a class="latest" href="{{ entry.latest.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <span class="meta">
              <span class="label">Latest post</span>
              {% if entry.latest.date %}<time class="date" datetime="{{ entry.latest.date }}">{{ entry.latest.date | format('D MMM YYYY') }}</time>{% endif %}
            </span>
            <span class="title">{{ entry.latest.title }}</span>
          </a>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        <span class="check" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="variant">
    <header>
      <h2>F — Minimal selectable row</h2>
      <p class="note">One-line density like the old D, but with homepage + RSS icons alongside the check. No latest post, no talk caption beyond the basics. Cheapest path to "pick feeds" if the latest-post block feels like too much.</p>
    </header>
    <div class="grid">
      {% for i in range(0, 4) %}
      {% set entry = speakerFeeds.entries[i] %}
      <div class="vf" data-toggle>
        <img src="{{ entry.photo }}" alt="" loading="lazy">
        <div class="who">
          <h3>{{ entry.name }}</h3>
          <p>{{ entry.talk.title }} · {{ entry.talk.year }}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="actions">
          <a class="icon-btn" href="{{ entry.homepage }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="{{ entry.name }}'s homepage" title="Homepage">{{ iconGlobe | safe }}</a>
          <a class="icon-btn" href="{{ entry.feed }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="{{ entry.name }}'s RSS feed" title="RSS feed">{{ iconRss | safe }}</a>
          <span class="check" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="variant">
    <header>
      <h2>D — Card-as-target</h2>
      <p class="note">Whole card is the selection target (click anywhere to toggle). One photo, one name, one muted talk-title caption, a check on the right. Built for the OPML picker flow — you're there to pick feeds, so make picking feel like the primary action.</p>
    </header>
    <div class="grid">
      {% for i in range(0, 4) %}
      {% set entry = speakerFeeds.entries[i] %}
      <div class="vd" data-toggle>
        <img src="{{ entry.photo }}" alt="" loading="lazy">
        <div class="who">
          <h3>{{ entry.name }}</h3>
          <p>{{ entry.talk.title }}</p>
        </div>
        <span class="check" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>
</section>

<script>
  document.querySelectorAll('[data-toggle]').forEach(el => {
    el.addEventListener('click', e => {
      if (e.target.closest('a')) return;
      el.classList.toggle('selected');
    });
  });
</script>
